** Create counter component:-
______________________________
** Create one folder inside components folder with the name of counter.
** Then create a file inside counter folder with the name of counter.jsx.
** Now we will create a function inside counter.jsx.
** Function will be like this:-
   Code:- import React  from "react";

          function Counter(){
          return(
        <div className="counter">
            Counter
        </div>
      );
   }
        export default Counter
		
01 Now we will import this counter inside App.js component.
   E.g:- import Counter  from './components/counters/Counter';

02 Now we will give the entry of counter inside App.js component.
   E.g:- <Counter></Counter>
   
03 Now hit the browser.   
04 Hopefully we are able to see the O/p.

   
		